Package: mlr3oml
Title: Connector between 'mlr3' and 'OpenML'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Michel",
             family = "Lang",
             role = c("cre", "aut"),
             email = "michellang@gmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9754-0393")))
Description: Provides an interface to 'OpenML.org' to download data and machine
  learning tasks. Tasks can be automatically converted to 'mlr3' tasks.
  For a more sophisticated interface which also supports listing and filtering
  of tasks as well as uploading experiments, see the 'OpenML' package.
License: LGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/mlr-org/mlr3oml
BugReports: https://github.com/mlr-org/mlr3oml
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    backports (>= 1.1.6),
    R6,
    checkmate,
    data.table,
    jsonlite,
    mlr3,
    mlr3misc,
    stringi
Suggests:
    qs,
    testthat
NeedsCompilation: yes
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
